---
title: Creamy Poblano Bolognese with Parmesan, Thyme, and Linguine
description: We’re amping up the classic Italian Bolognese with one of our favorite ingredients - the poblano pepper. This faintly spicy Mexican pepper adds the perfect kick to a comforting pasta classic.
